# JsonObject.TryGetValueInsensitive method

Try get value with insensitive case for key

```csharp
public bool TryGetValueInsensitive(string key, out object value)
```

| parameter | description |
| --- | --- |
| key | the key to get value from it |
| value | the value to return. Null if the value is not found |

## Return Value

True if the current JsonObject has a value for the current key, no matter the case. False otherwise.
